The l Isa location
End The l.

The o Isa object At l
  Container
End The o.

Syntax
  put_in = put (o) 'in' (c) Where c Isa container Else "You cannot put anything in" Say The c. "."

Add To Every object
  Verb put_in
    When o Does
      Locate o In c.
      "You put" Say The o. "in" Say The c. "."
      If o At l Then
        Look.
      Else
        Look.
      End If.
  End Verb.
End Add.

Start At l.
